Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.82,0:44:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}♪ 結ばれなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.49,0:44:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}♪ 愛を胸に生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.11,0:44:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}♪ これが私の道
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.12,0:44:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（４人）\N♪ Because now I got a way
